	<h3>School Bus Management System</h3>
	<p>This School Bus Management System enables both schools and
		parents to better plan and execute pick-up and drop of students.
		Parents are assisted with an SMS on the expected time of arrival (ETA)
		of school bus, as well as get confirmation SMS when their kids are
		dropped off or picked up from school.</p>
	<h4>Using This School Bus Management System you can:</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Reduce time of communication</li>
		<li>Identify contingencies early</li>
		<li>Understand the ETA of the school buses</li>
		<li>Also use as an attendance system</li>
	</ul>
</div>